Who's News:
   New Intelsat Director
   Adopts Decentralized
   Management Structure
John Hampton, 58, was named executive vice president of
operations and services. Mr. Hampton had been deputy director
general of operations and engineering. David Tudge, 58, was
made vice president and chief financial officer. He formerly
was deputy director general of services and administration.
Pierre Madon, 59, was appointed vice president of engineering
and research. He formerly was senior director of engineering
reporting to Mr. Hampton. Finally, the post of vice
president, information and administration was created, but
has yet to be filled.